== Degmadda Wanlaweyne (Daafeet) == 
----------------------------------------------
Degmada '''Wanlweyne''' (Daafeet) waa degmo katirsan degmooyinka Shabeellaha Hoose waxana hostaga tuulooyin farabadan oo garaya ila '''400''' tulo. Dhaqalaha dadka degmada ay kutirsan yihin waxaa kamida beeraha, iyo xoolaha nool. Degmadan waxaa kuyaala garonka caalamiga ee BALI-DOOGLE Airport... Odayaasha dhaqanka ayaa maamula degmada. 

Degmada w/wayne wa degmada kaliyaa ee beesha Hubeer ay aadka ugu badan yihin marki lo eego beelaha walaalahoda ee la degan. Degmada wanlaweyn wa xarunta ugu weyn ee beesha Hubeer degto marki lo eego gobolada Baay, Gedo, iyo Jubooyinka, maxa yeelay degmada w/weyn waxa ku noola shacab aad u xogan oo beesha u dhasheen wexeyna degmadasi ku leyihin goole odayal dhaqameed qadimi ah oo awood leh loona yaqano (Hubeer Hirine) oo marki af-maxaga lo fasiro la micno ah Hubeerka mideysaan ama isku xiran.

Gollaha odayasha dhaqanka ee Hubeer Hirinaha wuxu kaa koban yahay afarta laafod ee beesha Hubeer wexeyna Malaaq u caleemo-sareyn (Adan Xusein malaaq) oo dhaxal tooyo ku noqday malaqnimada sida dhaqanka beesha Hubeer u yahayba. Lakin inkastoo Malaq Adan Xusein Malaaq uu howlgab yahay kunna sugan yahay magalada muqdisho waxa howsha malaaqnimo u uu wakishaay duq sarkaalka ahna nabadoonka guud ee beesha Hubeer Nabadoon (Xusein Axmed Caliyow) oo ku suggan degmada wanlaweyne.

Gollaha odayasha ee Hubeer Hirinaha Daafeet waxa ay fasax siyeen in gobolada Alto-Jubba ay doran karan malaaq ayaga ugooni ah madama beeshu ay aad u balaran tahay, goboladasne ay aad uga fogyihin gobolka Sh/hoose oo ah xarunta malaaqa guud ee beesha Hubeer. Hadaba, xilka Malaqnimo ee gobolada alto-jubba ee beesha Hubeer waxa hada hayaa Malaaq Xasan Shurre Maxamuud ahna gudoomiyaha odayasha dhaqanka beelaha DigilMirifle.

Beesha Hubeer, dhaqan ahan malaaq wuxu kaga dhigan yahay abaandulle, oo mar walba u tagan difaaca shacabkisaa, iyo deganada beesha gud ahan. Hadaba, malaaqa guud ee beesha Hubeer waxa dhaqan ahan lagu caleemo saraa guriga yaranka bessha Hubeer ee Huliye ee Reereeji gar ahan Lafta Cumaroow qaasatan jufada reer Adde oo aad lo qadarriyo wanne lafta u malaaqa guud u ka amar qato wixi talo iyo tusaale ah maddama jufa Adde ee yihin dadka maalgeeliya beesha Hubeer daafeet hadi lacale beelo kale ay is qabtan.

Hadaba, malaaqa guud hadu lacale u duqobo ama howlgab noqdo, dhaqan ahan waxa uun codsankara in la bedelo jufada hose ee reer Adde. Haddi lacale lafaha qarkoda ee beesha Hubeer ka koban tahay ay isku qabsadan "Dooro biyoo macabto iyo way cabta" waxa la racaa talada jufada reer Adde oo ah halka ugu dambeyso ee garta lagu goyo. Dhaqankani ee beesha Hubeer ay ledahay wa dhaqan soojireen ah oo ay ku dhaqmi jireen kumaanan sano kahor.
Degmada w/weyn waxa lagu qiyaasay '''1 Milyaan qoys''' oo Hubeer wada ah hadi lagu darro dadka degan tulooyinka fog-fog ee xududaaha laaleh degmooyinka dariska ah.    

